711018f-a.title: Manhattan: 10th Street (East) - Avenue A
711018f-a.text:
East 10th Street, east from Ave., A. Note a portion of Tompkins
Scuare on the right. Promin3nt building shown on the far side of park, is
the new Christodora House, an east side settlement building.
May 21, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
Neg w R07
